::Spears::

She cried and rolled onto her back.  She felt the pain tear into her 
and it made her shake.  She looked and saw Striker down on the ground 
and not moving.  She looked up at Prebon.  Her eyes filled with water 
and her face with a pained expression. She could barely 
speak, "master Prebon, help him. please help him." She then closed 
her eyes and felt the tears roll down her face.  She looked back up 
at Prebon. "master, help me...it hurts." She then closed her eyes and 
winced as the pain sent shock waves through her body.  She finally 
passed out, laying in a pool of her own mech fluid.
